%% Diagram: Inventory reservation state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Available: Pre-sale stock loaded
    Available --> Reserved: Checkout start (atomic decrement)
    Reserved --> Confirmed: Payment success
    Reserved --> Available: Timeout or abandonment (return to pool)
    Confirmed --> [*]: Order durable
